OL,3,CTime to tax London tourists to help
OL,4,Cbankroll the capital?
OL,6,FBy Chris Howse: Programme and Digital
OL,7,FEditor
OL,9,FLondon's mayor wants to tax tourists
OL,10,Fto help the capital pay for big
OL,11,Finfrastructure projects and drive
OL,12,Feconomic growth.
OL,14,FAs the mayor's office turns 25, Sadiq
OL,15,FKhan believes more devolution would
OL,16,Fbenefit London instead of relying on
OL,17,Fthe government.
