OL,3,CTime to tax London tourists to help
OL,4,Cbankroll the capital?
OL,6,FAs well as a visitor levy on hotel
OL,7,Fguests the mayor wants to re-examine
OL,8,Fthe way transport is funded, control
OL,9,Fmore of the rail network and shake-up
OL,10,Fplanning rules to help build more
OL,11,Fhouses.
OL,13,F"We're speaking to the government
OL,14,Fabout what they can do in relation to
OL,15,Ffiscal devolution," London mayor Sadiq
OL,16,FKhan said.
OL,18,F"Can we use more powers to get
OL,19,Finfrastructure built in London? We've
OL,20,Fgot the Elizabeth Line, we've got the
OL,21,FNorthern Line extension
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
