OL,3,CTime to tax London tourists to help
OL,4,Cbankroll the capital?
OL,6,F"What about the Docklands Light
OL,7,FRailway extension to Thamesmead? Can
OL,8,Fwe use new powers to help pay for
OL,9,Fthese schemes?
OL,11,F"We're keen to make sure the
OL,12,Fgovernment understands that when we
OL,13,Fhave good policies they benefit in
OL,14,Fterms of extra taxes paid, jobs being
OL,15,Fcreated and so forth.
OL,17,F"We're keen to speak to the Government
OL,18,Fabout sharing the proceeds of some of
OL,19,Fthat growth," Mr Khan explained.
