OL,3,CTime to tax London tourists to help
OL,4,Cbankroll the capital?
OL,6,FResearch has shown that people prefer
OL,7,Fdecisions to be made closer to where
OL,8,Fthey live, according to Professor Tony
OL,9,FTravers from the London School of
OL,10,FEconomics.
OL,12,FHe believes one extra power in the
OL,13,Fshort term would be to take over the
OL,14,Fcommuter rail system inside London,
OL,15,Fsuch as Southereastern and Great
OL,16,FNorthern. London Metroisation, as it's
OL,17,Fcalled.
OL,19,FMr Travers also backed more powers to
OL,20,Fset taxes.
