OL,3,CTime to tax London tourists to help
OL,4,Cbankroll the capital?
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London already has
OL,7,Fconsiderable power, controlling public
OL,8,Ftransport and a big say in the police,
OL,9,Ffire service and major planning
OL,10,Fdecisions.
OL,12,FBut Andy Burnham, the mayor of Greater
OL,13,FManchester has more freedom than his
OL,14,Fopposite number in London when it
OL,15,Fcomes to spending government money.
OL,17,F"There are strengths and weaknesses in
OL,18,Fboth systems," Mr Burnham said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
