OL,3,CTime to tax London tourists to help
OL,4,Cbankroll the capital?
OL,6,F"But we've moved now to an integrated
OL,7,Fsettlement with the government where
OL,8,Fwe can allocate funding not according
OL,9,Fto what the Whitehall silos want, but
OL,10,Fmore flexibly across all of Greater
OL,11,FManchester, building from the bottom
OL,12,Fup with our councils," he added.
OL,14,FThe government is now deciding whether
OL,15,Fto devolve more powers to local
OL,16,Fauthorities.
